high_descs: Begin across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the stove.
Pick up the kettle that is on the front right burner of the stove.
Turn around and walk over to the sink.
Place the kettle into the sink basin and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the kettle.
Turn around and take a step forward, then right right and walk over to the stove.
Place the now clean kettle back onto the front right burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean kettle onto the stove.

high_descs: Walk forward to the counter then turn left and walk to the stove top.
Pick up the tea pot on the bottom right burner.
Turn around and walk to the sink to your left and stand in front of it facing it.
Clean the tea pot in the sink before picking it back up and turning off the tap.
Walk back to the stove top.
Put the tea pot back on the bottom right burner.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tea pot on the stove.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn to your left, walk straight to the stove
Pick up the kettle on the right side of the stove
Turn to your right and head to the sink
Place the kettle on the sink and rinse it
Pick up the kettle, turn around and head back to the stove
Put the kettle on the right side of the stove in front of the first knob
anns.task_desc: Put the clean kettle on the stove
